[div class=p 
	"IRC is short for Internet Relay Chat. It's a protocol that allows people to chat with one another by means of a chatroom. As such, it's very easy to discuss speedrun projects with each other when you're able to directly converse (although most of the time, the ongoing conversation is similar to that of the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Off topic forum|href=/Forum/Subforum/4)
	").
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Feel free to join the TASVideos private IRC channel, located at 
	[code 
		"#tasvideos
	]code
	" on 
	[code 
		"irc.libera.chat
	]code
	".
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"If you have an IRC client, 
	[a href=irc://irc.libera.chat/tasvideos rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"you may simply click this link
	]a
	". The link will not work if you don't have one yet.
	$LF
]div
